
Dzawuwu afahyɛ yɛ afe afe ammamerɛ ne nnaseɛ afahyɛ a a ahenfo ne wɔn manfo a wɔn wɔ Agave a ɛwɔ Dabala, wɔ Frao Mantam no di wɔ Ghana. Wodi saa afahyɛ yi wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so mienu no mu.

== Afa hyɛ ==
Wɔ afahyɛ no bere mu no, wonoa aduane sorɔnko bi a wɔpete ma abaosom no de srɛ ahobammɔ ma ɔmanfo no. Wɔgu nsa na amanfo taa wɔn ahenfo no akyi.

== Mfaso ==
It is celebrated to mark the bravery of the Agaves in the past who fought and won several wars. It is the time to pay homage to those who have departed.

